		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em>Weapon (Mace) - Rare (Requires Attunement)</em></p><p><strong>Activation</strong> - 3 Charges (Regains 1d3 Charges at Dawn)</p><ul><li><p>Action (1 Charge) - Release a wave of terror. Each creature of your choice within 30 feet makes a [[/save WIS 15]]{DC 15 Wisdom saving throw} or has the &amp;Reference[Frightened apply=false] condition for 1 minute. While Frightened this way, a creature must spend its turn moving as far from you as it can and can&#39;t make Opportunity Attacks. It can use only the Dash action or attempt to escape from an effect that prevents movement; if it can&#39;t move, it can take the Dodge action. Affected creatures repeat the save at the end of each of their turns, ending the effect on themselves on a success.</p></li></ul>",
